        "synopsis": {
            "value": "On a cruise to the Bahamas, shy administrative assistant Chen Jia Xin and charming heir Wang Xi Yi have a one-night stand, complicated by a mix-up in identities. When Jia Xin becomes pregnant, she’s pressured into a marriage with Xi Yi, who plans to marry his girlfriend, Shi Anna. A tragic misunderstanding drives Jia Xin to Hungary, where she becomes a potter with the support of her friend Dylan. Three years later,\n\nXi Yi has matured and realizes his desire for a family. Fate reunites them in Hungary, where love has a second chance.",
